name: chikorita
flavor_text_en: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on itshead. It is docile and loves to soak up the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
flavor_text_en: The scent of spices comes from around its neck.Somehow, sniffing it makes you want to fight.

name: meganium
flavor_text_en: The aroma that rises from its petals contains asubstance that calms aggressive feelings.

name: cyndaquil
flavor_text_en: It has a timid nature. If it is startled, the flames on its back burn more vigorously.

name: quilava
flavor_text_en: Be careful if it turns its back during battle. Itmeans that it will attack with the fire on its back.

name: typhlosion
flavor_text_en: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything thattouches it will instantly go up in flames.

name: totodile
flavor_text_en: Its well-developed jaws are powerful and capable ofcrushing anything. Even its trainer must be careful.

name: croconaw
flavor_text_en: If it loses a fang, a new one grows back in itsplace. There are always 48 fangs lining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
flavor_text_en: When it bites with its massive and powerful jaws, itshakes its head and savagely tears its victim up.

name: sentret
flavor_text_en: A very cautious POKéMON, it raises itself up usingits tail to get a better view of its surroundings.

name: furret
flavor_text_en: It makes a nest to suit its long and skinny body. Thenest is impossible for other POKéMON to enter.

name: hoothoot
flavor_text_en: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet sofast, the movement can rarely be seen.

name: noctowl
flavor_text_en: Its eyes are specially adapted. They concentrateeven faint light and enable it to see in the dark.

name: ledyba
flavor_text_en: It is very timid. It will be afraid to move if it isalone. But it will be active if it is in a group.

name: ledian
flavor_text_en: When the stars flicker in the night sky, itflutters about, scattering a glowing powder.

name: spinarak
flavor_text_en: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web,waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ariados
flavor_text_en: It spins string not only from its rear but also fromits mouth. It is hard to tell which end is which.

name: crobat
flavor_text_en: It flies so si­ lently through the dark on its fourwings that it may not be noticed even when nearby.

name: chinchou
flavor_text_en: Chinchou blink their shining antennae at one another to claim their respective turf.

name: lanturn
flavor_text_en: The light it emits is so bright that it can illuminatethe sea's surface from a depth of over three miles.

name: pichu
flavor_text_en: It is not yet skilled at storing electricity.It may send out a jolt if amused or startled.

name: cleffa
flavor_text_en: Because of its unusual, star-like silhouette, peoplebelieve that it came here on a meteor.

name: igglybuff
flavor_text_en: It has a very soft body. If it starts to roll, it willbounce all over and be impossible to stop.

name: togepi
flavor_text_en: The shell seems to be filled with joy. It is saidthat it will share good luck when treated kindly.

name: togetic
flavor_text_en: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, car­ing people and shower them with happiness.

name: natu
flavor_text_en: Because its wings aren't yet fully grown, it has tohop to get around. It is always star­ ing at something.

name: xatu
flavor_text_en: They say that it stays still and quiet because itis seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: mareep
flavor_text_en: If static elec­ tricity builds in its body, itsfleece doubles in volume. Touching it will shock you.

name: flaaffy
flavor_text_en: As a result of storing too much electricity, itdeveloped patches where even downy wool won't grow.

name: ampharos
flavor_text_en: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seenfrom far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

name: bellossom
flavor_text_en: Plentiful in the tropics. When it dances, its petals rub together and make a pleasant ringing sound.

name: marill
flavor_text_en: The tip of its tail, which con­ tains oil that islighter than wa­ ter, lets it swim without drowning.

name: azumarill
flavor_text_en: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.

name: sudowoodo
flavor_text_en: Although it always pretends to be a tree, its composi­tion appears to be closer to a rock than a plant.

name: politoed
flavor_text_en: If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, theyrespond by gather­ ing from far and wide.

name: hoppip
flavor_text_en: To keep from being blown away by the wind, they gatherin clusters. They do enjoy gentle breezes, though.

name: skiploom
flavor_text_en: The bloom on top of its head opens and closes as thetemperature fluc­ tuates up and down.

name: jumpluff
flavor_text_en: Once it catches the wind, it deft­ ly controls itscotton-puff spores to float, even around the world.

name: aipom
flavor_text_en: Its tail is so powerful that it can use it to graba tree branch and hold itself up in the air.

name: sunkern
flavor_text_en: It may drop out of the sky suddenly. If attacked by aSPEAROW, it will violently shake its leaves.

name: sunflora
flavor_text_en: It converts sun­ light into energy. In the darknessafter sunset, it closes its petals and becomes still.

name: yanma
flavor_text_en: If it flaps its wings really fast, it can generateshock waves that will shatter win­ dows in the area.

name: wooper
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON lives in cold water. It will leave thewater to search for food when it gets cold outside.

name: quagsire
flavor_text_en: This carefree POKéMON has an easy-going nature.While swimming, it always bumps into boat hulls.

name: espeon
flavor_text_en: It uses the fine hair that covers its body to senseair currents and predict its ene­ my's actions.

name: umbreon
flavor_text_en: When agitated, this POKéMON pro­ tects itself byspraying poisonous sweat from its pores.

name: murkrow
flavor_text_en: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bringmisfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: slowking
flavor_text_en: It has incredible intellect and in­ tuition. Whateverthe situation, it remains calm and collected.

name: misdreavus
flavor_text_en: It likes playing mischievous tricks such as screamingand wailing to startle people at night.

name: unown
flavor_text_en: Their shapes look like hieroglyphs on ancient tab­lets. It is said that the two are somehow related.

name: wobbuffet
flavor_text_en: It hates light and shock. If attack­ ed, it inflatesits body to pump up its counter­ strike.

name: girafarig
flavor_text_en: Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! Ifyou get close, it may react to your scent and bite.

name: pineco
flavor_text_en: It likes to make its shell thicker by adding layersof tree bark. The additional weight doesn't bother it.

name: forretress
flavor_text_en: Its entire body is shielded by a steel-hard shell.What lurks inside the armor is a total mystery.

name: dunsparce
flavor_text_en: When spotted, this POKéMON escapes backward by furi­ously boring into the ground with its tail.

name: gligar
flavor_text_en: It flies straight at its target's face then clampsdown on the star­ tled victim to inject poison.

name: steelix
flavor_text_en: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.

name: snubbull
flavor_text_en: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind andaffectionate. It is very popular among women.

name: granbull
flavor_text_en: It is actually timid and easily spooked. If at­tacked, it flails about to fend off its attacker.

name: qwilfish
flavor_text_en: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its bodyby drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

name: scizor
flavor_text_en: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

name: shuckle
flavor_text_en: The BERRIES it stores in its vase-like shelldecompose and become a gooey liquid.

name: heracross
flavor_text_en: It is usually docile, but if it is disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn.

name: sneasel
flavor_text_en: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sud­denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

name: teddiursa
flavor_text_en: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It alwayslicks its paws because they are soaked with honey.

name: ursaring
flavor_text_en: Although it is a good climber, it prefers to snaptrees with its forelegs and eat fallen BERRIES.

name: slugma
flavor_text_en: It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because ifit stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.

name: magcargo
flavor_text_en: The shell on its back is just skin that has cooledand hardened. It breaks easily with a slight touch.

name: swinub
flavor_text_en: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig upfood. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

name: piloswine
flavor_text_en: Because the long hair all over its body obscures itssight, it just keeps charging repeatedly.

name: corsola
flavor_text_en: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of itshead is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

name: remoraid
flavor_text_en: It has superb ac­ curacy. The water it shoots out canstrike even moving prey from more than 300 feet.

name: octillery
flavor_text_en: It traps enemies with its suction- cupped tentaclesthen smashes them with its rock-hard head.

name: delibird
flavor_text_en: It carries food all day long. There are talesabout lost people who were saved by the food it had.

name: mantine
flavor_text_en: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if REMORAIDattach to it for scavenging its leftovers.

name: skarmory
flavor_text_en: Its sturdy wings look heavy, but they are actuallyhollow and light, allowing it to fly freely in the sky.

name: houndour
flavor_text_en: It uses different kinds of cries for communicating withothers of its kind and for pursuing its prey.

name: houndoom
flavor_text_en: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from itsmouth, the pain will never go away.

name: kingdra
flavor_text_en: It is said that it usually hides in underwater caves.It can create whirlpools by yawning.

name: phanpy
flavor_text_en: It swings its long snout around play­ fully, but becauseit is so strong, that can be dan­ gerous.

name: donphan
flavor_text_en: It has sharp, hard tusks and a rugged hide. Its TACKLEis strong enough to knock down a house.

name: porygon2
flavor_text_en: This upgraded version of PORYGON is designed forspace exploration. It can't fly, though.

name: stantler
flavor_text_en: The curved antlers subtly change the flow of air tocreate a strange space where real­ ity is distorted.

name: smeargle
flavor_text_en: A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. Itpaints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.

name: tyrogue
flavor_text_en: It is always bursting with en­ ergy. To make it­self stronger, it keeps on fighting even if it loses.

name: hitmontop
flavor_text_en: If you become enchanted by its smooth, elegant,dance-like kicks, you may get drilled hard.

name: smoochum
flavor_text_en: Its lips are the most sensitive parts on its body.It always uses its lips first to examine things.

name: elekid
flavor_text_en: It rotates its arms to generate electricity, butit tires easily, so it charges up only a little bit.

name: magby
flavor_text_en: Each and every time it inhales and exhales, hotembers dribble out of its mouth and nostrils.

name: miltank
flavor_text_en: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it theultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

name: blissey
flavor_text_en: Anyone who takes even one bite of BLISSEY's egg be­comes unfailingly caring and pleas­ ant to everyone.

name: raikou
flavor_text_en: The rain clouds it carries let it fire thunderboltsat will. They say that it descended with lightning.

name: entei
flavor_text_en: Volcanoes erupt when it barks. Un­ able to restrainits extreme power, it races headlong around the land.

name: suicune
flavor_text_en: It races around the world to purify fouled water. It dashes away with the north wind.

name: larvitar
flavor_text_en: It feeds on soil. After it has eaten a large mountain,it will fall asleep so it can grow.

name: pupitar
flavor_text_en: Its shell is as hard as sheet rock, and it isalso very strong. Its THRASHING can topple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
flavor_text_en: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so itis very eager to make challenges against enemies.

name: lugia
flavor_text_en: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at thebottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

name: ho-oh
flavor_text_en: Legends claim this POKéMON flies the world's skies con­tinuously on its magnificent seven- colored wings.

name: celebi
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON wan­ ders across time. Grass and treesflourish in the forests in which it has appeared.
